  "title": "Part-time Piano Instructor",
  "description": "<p>JOB DESCRIPTION</p>\n<p><strong>Industry</strong></p>\n<p>Training courses for music, dancing, art, speech and drama</p>\n<p><strong>Job Title</strong></p>\n<p>Part-time Piano Instructor</p>\n<p><strong>Occupation</strong></p>\n<p>PIANO INSTRUCTOR (EXTRACURRICULUM)</p>\n<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><strong>LEVEL UP YOUR PIANO/POP-PIANO COACHING AT LWS – TEAM UP WITH MANDOPOP PROS!</strong></p>\n<p>Hey, if you're passionate about piano and got that hustle vibe, listen up – LWS Music Academy's got an awesome opportunity for our 30th anniversary. We're growing the Mandopop world, and we'd love you to mentor emerging talents, collab with industry experts, and boost your own career.</p>\n<p><strong>What You'll Get:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Part-time roles: Make an impact on tons of students in Singapore's Mandopop hub.</li>\n  <li>Solid network: Connect with pros, get exclusive resources, grow your brand.</li>\n  <li>Real results: Our grads hit the charts – shape theirs and level up yours.</li>\n  <li>Ideal fits: 3+ years teaching vocals, music diploma, your own releases, stage experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Open to Singapore citizens and Permanent Residents only</li>\n  <li>Hold a relevant diploma or bachelor's degree in music</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of piano teaching experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Spots won't last – apply now! Send CV, cover letter, portfolio to ask@leeweisong.com.sg. Let's build together at 8 Raffles Ave., #02-12 Esplanade Mall, Singapore 039802.</p>\n<p>Join the hustle. Share your voice.</p>",
